 their journey in Paris.Galaxy AIis at the forefront of the user experience, and Samsung hopes that athletes will find features like Live Translation, Interpreter, and Composer useful.In addition, athletes will benefit from 100GB 5G data from Orange, which will be preloaded on an eSIM, and two years of global warranty.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3047884197374671e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Galaxy Z Flip\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\"}, {\"begin\": 1223, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0145804755603644e-13, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q483045