ge_S.A.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6008233848774986e-24, \"text\": \"Orange\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good reason\", \"from\": 9846, \"to\": 9859}, {\"ngram\": \"this early access\", \"from\": 9864, \"to\": 9881}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 9886, \"to\": 9895}, {\"ngram\": \"a much bigger role\", \"from\": 9949, \"to\": 9967}, {\"ngram\": \"its predecessors\", \"from\": 9980, \"to\": 9996}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 10066, \"to\": 10074}, {\"ngram\": \"early access\", \"from\": 10075, \"to\": 10087}, {\"ngram\": \"their journey\", \"from\": 10160, \"to\": 10173}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 10177, \"to\": 10182}, {\"ngram\": \"Galaxy AIis\", \"from\": 10183, \"to\": 10194}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 10198, \"to\": 10211}, {\"ngram\": \"the user experience\", \"from\": 10215, \"to\": 10234}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 10259, \"to\": 10267}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 10278, \"to\": 10286}, {\"ngram\": \"Live Translation\", \"from\": 10292, \"to\": 10308}, {\"ngram\": \"Interpreter\", \"from\": 10310, \"to\": 10321}, {\"ngram\": \"Composer\", \"from\": 10327, \"to\": 10335}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 10346, \"to\": 10354}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 10356, \"to\": 10364}, {\"ngram\": \"100GB 5G data\", \"from\": 10383, \"to\": 10396}, {\"ngram\": \"an eSIM\", \"from\": 10437, \"to\": 10444}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 10450, \"to\": 10459}, {\"ngram\": \"global warranty\", \"from\": 10463, \"to\": 10478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The phone also comes with official IOC apps, including Athlete365, Olympic Shop, Paris 2024, Transport Accred App, and IOC hotline.Furthermore, thanks to a partnership with The Coca-Cola Company, athletes can useSamsung Walletto get free beverages from vending machines located throughout the Olympic and Paralympic Village.Likewise, through a partnership with Ile-de-France Mobilites, Samsung will give athletes an unlimited public transport access card with which they can tour Paris.As for the phone itself, Samsung describes the Galaxy Z Flip 6 Olympic Edition as having a striking yellow colorway with Olympic rings and the Paralympic Agitos logo in gold.Our story continues after the Galaxy Z Flip 6 hands-on video\\u2026Aside from the unique finish, Samsung also partnered with Parisian Men's Luxury House Berluti, who designed Team France's official Paris 2024 outfits, to create a FlipSuite Case made from Venezia leather.A first in the Olympic and Paralympic Games historyIn 2024, Samsung went one extra step to make the exclusive Olympic Edition smartphone even more special than ever.\", \"from\": 10480, \"to\": 11570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10515, \"end\": 10518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3047884197374671e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 10561, \"end\": 10571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999989295247, \"rank\": 1.0704818935517578e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 10653, \"end\": 10674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"score\": 0.9954048576273143, \"rank\": 0.0046163551821736554, \"text\": \"The Coca-Cola Company\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\"}, {\"begin\": 10841, \"end\": 10854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00ce