{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 11794, \"to\": 11806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As such, traditionally, the podium was always photographed by accredited media from afar.However, this year, for the first time in history, the IOC will allow athletes to bring their phones, i.e., the Galaxy Z Flip 6 Olympic Edition, to the Paris 2024 podium, where they will take selfies and upload them in real-time to the official Athlete365 app.There is no sign that Samsung will ever sell this exclusive phone to the general public.\", \"from\": 11808, \"to\": 12245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11952, \"end\": 11955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3047884197374671e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 12009, \"end\": 12022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Galaxy Z Flip\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\"}, {\"begin\": 12049, \"end\": 12059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999989295247, \"rank\": 1.0704818935517578e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 12179, \"end\": 12186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0145804755603644e-13, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 11832, \"to\":