"ngram\": \"one extra step\", \"from\": 13900, \"to\": 13914}, {\"ngram\": \"the exclusive Olympic Edition\", \"from\": 13923, \"to\": 13952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, for the first time in the history of the Olympic and Paralympic Games history, a smartphone will be present on the podium.The usual rules state that athletes can not bring personal belongings, such as phones, to the ceremony.\", \"from\": 13993, \"to\": 14229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 14008, \"to\": 14022}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 14026, \"to\": 14037}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games history\", \"from\": 14041, \"to\": 14081}, {\"ngram\": \"a smartphone\", \"from\": 14083, \"to\": 14095}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 14115, \"to\": 14125}, {\"ngram\": \"The usual rules\", \"from\": 14126, \"to\": 14141}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 14153, \"to\": 14161}, {\"ngram\": \"personal belongings\", \"from\": 14176, \"to\": 14195}, {\"ngram\": \"phones\", \"from\": 14205, \"to\": 14211}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 14216, \"to\": 14228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As such, traditionally, the podium was always photographed by accredited media from afar.However, this year, for the first time in history, the IOC will allow athletes to bring their phones, i.e., the Galaxy Z Flip 6 Olympic Edition, to the Paris 2024 podium, where they will take selfies and upload them in real-time to the official Athlete365 app.There is no sign that Samsung will ever sell this exclusive phone to the general public.\", \"from\": 14230, \"to\": 14667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14374, \"end\": 14377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3047884197374671e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Comm