.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999381544, \"rank\": 5.993146914763798e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the standard Galaxy Z Flip\", \"from\": 14727, \"to\": 14753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not offer free beverages and transport passes through the Wallet app but boasts the same Galaxy AI capabilities and fantastic design.\", \"from\": 14757, \"to\": 14898, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free beverages\", \"from\": 14775, \"to\": 14789}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 14794, \"to\": 14803}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wallet app\", \"from\": 14819, \"to\": 14833}, {\"ngram\": \"the same Galaxy AI capabilities\", \"from\": 14845, \"to\": 14876}, {\"ngram\": \"fantastic design\", \"from\": 14881, \"to\": 14897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, athletes will benefit from 100GB 5G data from Orange, which will be preloaded on an eSIM, and two years of global warranty.\", \"from\": 14900, \"to\": 15036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14959, \"end\": 14965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6008233848774986e-24, \"text\": \"Orange\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 14903, \"to\": 14911}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 14913, \"to\": 14921}, {\"ngram\": \"100GB 5G data\", \"from\": 14940, \"to\": 14953}, {\"ngram\": \"an eSIM\", \"from\": 14994, \"to\": 15001}, {\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 15007, \"to\": 15016}, {\"ngram\": \"global warranty\", \"from\": 15020, \"to\": 15035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The phone also comes with official IOC apps, including Athlete365, Olympic Shop, Paris 2024, Transport Accred App, and IOC hotline.Furt