esource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 16389, \"to\": 16399}, {\"ngram\": \"accredited media\", \"from\": 16427, \"to\": 16443}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 16478, \"to\": 16492}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 16496, \"to\": 16503}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 16524, \"to\": 16532}, {\"ngram\": \"their phones\", \"from\": 16542, \"to\": 16554}, {\"ngram\": \"selfies\", \"from\": 16646, \"to\": 16653}, {\"ngram\": \"real-time\", \"from\": 16673, \"to\": 16682}, {\"ngram\": \"the official Athlete365 app\", \"from\": 16686, \"to\": 16713}, {\"ngram\": \"no sign\", \"from\": 16723, \"to\": 16730}, {\"ngram\": \"this exclusive phone\", \"from\": 16759, \"to\": 16779}, {\"ngram\": \"the general public\", \"from\": 16783, \"to\": 16801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are not an Olympian, you can at least pre-order the standard Galaxy Z Flip 6.\", \"from\": 16803, \"to\": 16891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16825, \"end\": 16833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999381544, \"rank\": 5.993146914763798e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the standard Galaxy Z Flip\", \"from\": 16862, \"to\": 16888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not offer free beverages and transport passes through the Wallet app but boasts the same Galaxy AI capabilities and fantastic design.\", \"from\": 16892, \"to\": 17033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free beverages\", \"from\": 16910, \"to\": 16924}, {\"ngram\": \"transport\", \"from\": 16929, \"to\": 16938}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wallet app\", \"from\": 16954, \"to\": 16968}, {\"ngram\": \"the same Galaxy AI capabilities\", \"from\": 16980, \"to\": 17011}, {\"ngram\": \"fantastic design\", \"from\": 17016, \"to\": 17032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, thanks to a partnership with The Coca-Cola Company, athletes can useSamsung Walletto get free beverages from vending machines located throughout the Olympic and Paralympic Village.Likewise, through a partnership with Ile-de-France Mobilites, Samsung will give athletes an unlimited public transport access card with which they can tour Paris.As for the phone itself, Samsung describes the Galaxy Z Flip 6 Olympic Edition as having a striking yellow colorway with Olympic rings and the Paralympic Agitos logo in gold.Our story continues after the Galaxy Z Flip 6 hands-on video\\u2026Aside from the unique finish, Samsung also partnered with Parisian Men's Luxury House Berluti, who designed Team France's official Paris 2024 outfits, to create a FlipSuite Case made from Venezia leather.A first in the Olympic and Paralympic Games historyIn 2024, Samsung went one extra step to make the exclusive Olympic Edition smartphone even more special than ever.\", \"from\": 17035, \"to\": 17994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17077, \"end\": 17098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"score\": 0.9954048576273143, \"rank\": 0.0046163551821736554, \"text\": \"The Coca-Cola Company\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\"}, {\"begin\": 17265, \"end\": 17278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\", \"score\": 0.9997562403124285, \"rank\": 0.0002438190999641094, \"text\": \"Ile-de-France\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00cele-de-France\"}, {\"begin\": 17290, \"end\": 17297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0145804755603644e-13, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/